      {
        "title": "Illusionist",
        "excerpt": "Powers          Name     Tier     Type     Description                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      Color Spray                  Novice                                                                                                             Illusory Disguise                  Novice                                                                                                             Illusory Object                  Novice                                                                                                             Invisibility                  Novice                                                                                                             Phantom Pain                  Novice                                                                                                             Illusory Scene                  Veteran                                                                                     Phantasmal Killer                  Veteran                                                                                                             Shadow Siphon                  Veteran                                                                                                             Project Image                  Master                                                                                                             Weird                  Epic                                                                                     Charming Words                  Novice                                                                                                             Command                  Novice                                                                                                             Fear                  Novice                                                                                                             Confusion                  Veteran                                                                                                             Mind Reading                  Veteran                                                                                                             Suggestion                  Veteran                                                                                                             Synaptic Pulse                  Veteran                                                                                                             Dominate                  Master                                                                                                             Warp Mind                  Master                                                                                                             Fabricated Truth                  Epic                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        Color Spray                                   Novice                            Incapacitation              Spell              Visual                                Cost         1 Mana              Area         15-foot cone              Save         Will              Duration         1 or more rounds                  Swirling colors affect viewers based on their Will saves.                       Critical Success         The creature is unaffected                   Success         The creature is dazzled for 1 round                   Failure         The creature is stunned 1, blinded for 1 round, and dazzled for 1 minute                   Critical Failure         The creature is stunned for 1 round and blinded for 1 minute                                    Illusory Disguise                                   Novice                            Spell              Visual                                Cost         1 Mana              Duration         1 hour                  You create an illusion that causes you to appear as another creature of the same body shape, and with roughly similar height and weight as yourself. The disguise is typically good enough to hide your identity, but not to impersonate a specific individual. The spell doesn’t change your voice, scent, or mannerisms. You can change the appearance of your clothing and worn items, but held items are unaffected, and any worn item you remove returns to its true appearance.      Heightened (total 2 Mana)   The spell also disguises your voice and scent, and it gains the Auditory trait   Heightened (total 3 Mana)   You can appear as any creature of the same size, even a specific individual as long as you’ve seen them before   Heightened (total 6 Mana)   You can target up to 10 creatures within 30 feet                             Illusory Object                                   Novice                            Visual              Spell                                Cost         1 Mana              Range         500 feet              Area         20-foot burst              Duration         10 minutes                  You create an illusory visual image of a stationary object. The entire image must fit within the spell’s area. The object appears to animate naturally, but it doesn’t make sounds or generate smells. Any creature that touches the image or uses the Seek action to examine it can attempt to disbelieve your illusion.      Heightened (total 2 Mana)   Your image makes appropriate sounds, generates normal smells, and feels right to the touch. The spell gains the Auditory trait. The duration increases to 1 hour.   Heightened (total 5 Mana)   The duration is unlimited.                             Invisibility                                   Novice                            Spell                                Cost         2 Mana              Range         Touch              Duration         10 minutes                  Cloaked in illusion, the target becomes invisible. This makes it hidden from all creatures that rely on sight. If the target uses a hostile action, the spell ends after that action is completed.      Heightened (total 4 Mana)   The spell lasts 1 minute, but it doesn’t end if the target uses a hostile action                             Phantom Pain                                   Novice                            Mental              Spell                                Cost         1 Mana              Range         30 feet              Save         Will              Duration         1 minute                  Illusory pain wracks the target, dealing 2d4 mental damage and 1d4 persistent mental damage. The target must attempt a Will save.                       Critical Success         The target is unaffected                   Success         The target takes full initial damage but no persistent damage, and the spell ends immediately                   Failure         The target takes full initial and persistent damage, and the target is sickened 1                   Critical Failure         As failure, but the target is sickened 2                                    Illusory Scene                         Veteran                              Prerequisites         Illusory Object                  Your Illusory Object power can form a scene that includes up to 10 moving creatures or objects. You can have each part of the scene follow a repeating program up to 1 minute long. A creature that interacts with one part of your image only disbelieves that portion.                             Phantasmal Killer                                   Veteran                            Death              Emotion              Fear              Mental              Spell                                Cost         4 Mana              Range         120 feet              Save         Will                  You create a phantasmal image of the most fearsome creature imaginable to the target. Only the spell’s target can see the killer, though you can see the vague shape of the illusion as it races forth to attack. The effect of the killer is based on the outcome of the target’s Will save.      Heightened (per +1 Mana)   The damage increases by 1d6 on a success, by 2d6 on a failure, and by 3d6 on a critical failure                       Critical Success         The target is unaffected                   Success         The target takes 4d6 mental damage and is frightened 1                   Failure         The target takes 8d6 mental damage and is frightened 2                   Critical Failure         The target is so afraid it might die. It must attempt a Fortitude save (with the Incapacitation trait); if the target fails, it dies. On a successful Fortitude save, the target takes 12d6 mental damage, is fleeing until the end of its next turn, and is frightened 4.                                    Shadow Siphon                                   Veteran                            Shadow              Spell                                Cost         5 Mana              Range         60 feet              Trigger         A spell or magical effect within range deals damage                  Exchanging material energy with shadows, you transform the triggering spell into a partially illusory version of itself. Any creatures that would be damaged by the spell instead take only half as much damage, but the spell otherwise works as normal.                             Project Image                                   Master                            Mental              Spell                                Cost         7 Mana              Range         30 feet              Duration         Sustained up to 1 minute                  You project an illusory image of yourself. You must stay within range of the image, and if at any point you can’t see the image, the spell ends. Whenever you cast a spell, you can cause the spell effect to originate from either yourself or the image. Because the image is an illusion, it isn’t a creature and can’t benefit from spells. The image has the same AC and saves as you. If it is hit by an attack or fails a save, the spell ends.      Heightened (total 9 Mana)   The maximum duration you can Sustan the spell increases to 10 minutes                             Weird                         Epic                              Prerequisites         Phantasmal Killer                  When you spend at least 8 Mana on Phantasmal Killer, the spell targets any number of creatures within range.                             Charming Words                                   Novice                            Auditory              Incapacitation              Linguistic              Mental              Spell                                Cost         1 Mana              Range         30 feet              Save         Will              Duration         Until the start of your next turn                  You whisper enchanting words to deflect your foe’s ire. The target must attempt a Will save.                       Critical Success         The target is unaffected                   Success         The target takes a -1 penalty to attack rolls and damage rolls against you                   Failure         The target can’t use hostile actions against you                   Critical Failure         The target is stunned 1 and can’t use hostile actions against you                                    Command                                   Novice                            Auditory              Linguistic              Mental              Spell                                Cost         1 Mana              Range         30 feet              Save         Will              Duration         Until the end of the target’s next turn                  You shout a command that’s hard to ignore. You can command the target to approach you, run away (as if it had the fleeing condition), release what it’s holding, drop prone, or stand in place. It can’t Delay or take any reactions until it has obeyed your command. The effects depend on the target’s Will save.      Heightened (total 5 Mana)   You can target up to 10 creatures                            Success         The creature is unaffected                   Failure         For the first action on its next turn, the creature must use a single action to do as you command                   Critical Failure         The target must use all its actions on its next turn to obey your command                                    Fear                                   Novice                            Emotion              Fear              Mental              Spell                                Cost         1 Mana              Range         30 feet              Save         Will              Duration         1 minute                  You plant fear in the target; it must attempt a Will save.      Heightened (total 3 Mana)   You can target up to five creatures                       Critical Success         The target is unaffected                   Success         The target is frightened 1                   Failure         The target is frightened 2                   Critical Failure         The target is frightened 3 for the duration, and is fleeing for 1 round                                    Confusion                                   Veteran                            Emotion              Mental              Spell                                Cost         4 Mana              Range         30 feet              Save         Will                  You befuddle your target with strange impulses, causing it to act randomly. The effects are determined by the target’s Will save. You can Dismiss the spell.      Heightened (total 8 Mana)   You can target up to 10 creatures                       Critical Success         The target is unaffected                   Success         The target babbles incoherently and is stunned 1                   Failure         The target is confused for 1 minute, and can attempt a new save at the end of each of its turns to end the confusion                   Critical Failure         The target is confused for 1 minute, with no save to end the effect early                                    Mind Reading                                   Veteran                            Divination              Mental              Spell                                Cost         3 Mana              Range         30 feet              Save         Will              Duration         1 round, or sustained up to 1 minute                  With a cursory mental touch, you attempt to read the target’s mind. It must attempt a Will save. The target then becomes temporarily immune to your Mind Reading power for 1 hour.                       Critical Success         The target perceives vague surface thoughts from you                   Success         You find out whether the target’s Intelligence is higher than, equal to, or lower than yours                   Failure         You perceive vague surface thoughts from the target, and you find out whether its Intelligence is higher than, equal to, or lower than yours                   Critical Failure         As failure, and for the duration of the spell, you can Sustain to detect the target’s surface throughts again                                    Suggestion                                   Veteran                            Incapacitation              Linguistic              Mental              Spell                                Cost         4 Mana              Range         30 feet              Save         Will              Duration         Varies                  Your honeyed words are difficult for creatures to resist. You suggest a course of action to the target, which must be phrased in such a way as to seem like a logical course of action to the target and can’t be self-destructive or obviously against the target’s self-interest. The target must attempt a Will save.      Heightened (total 5 Mana)   You can implant the suggestion in the target’s subconscious, waiting for a trigger you specify. The first time the trigger occurs during the next 24 hours, the target immediately follows your suggestion.   Heightened (total 8 Mana)   You can target up to 10 creatures                       Critical Success         The target is unaffected and knows you tried to control it                   Success         The target is unaffected and thinks you were talking to them normally, not casting a spell on them                   Failure         The target immediately follows your suggestion. The spell has a duration of 1 minute, or until the target has completeda a finite suggestion or the suggestion becomes self-destructive or has other obvious negative effects.                   Critical Failure         As failure, but the base duration is 1 hour                                    Synaptic Pulse                                   Veteran                            Incapacitation              Mental              Spell                                Cost         5 Mana              Range         30 feet              Area         30-foot emanation              Save         Will              Duration         1 round                  You emit a pulsating mental blast that penetrates the minds of all enemies in the area. Each creature in the area must attempt a Will save.                       Critical Success         The creature is unaffected                   Success         The creature is stunned 1                   Failure         The creature is stunned 2                   Critical Failure         The creature is stunned for 1 round                                    Dominate                                   Master                            Incapacitation              Mental              Spell                                Cost         6 Mana              Range         30 feet              Save         Will              Duration         24 hours                  You take command of the target, forcing it to obey your orders. If you issue an obviously self-destructive order, the target doesn’t act until you issue a new order. The effect depends on its Will save.      Heightened (total 10 Mana)   The duration is unlimited                       Critical Success         The target is unaffected                   Success         The target is stunned 1 as it fights off your commands                   Failure         The target follows your orders but can attempt a Will save at the end of each of its turns. On a success, the spell ends.                   Critical Failure         As a failure, but the target receives a new save only when you give it a new order that is against its nature, such as killing its allies.                                    Warp Mind                                   Master                            Emotion              Incapacitation              Mental              Spell                                Cost         7 Mana              Range         120 feet              Save         Will                  You scramble a creature’s mental faculties and sensory input. The target must attempt a Will saving throw. Regardless of the result of that save, the target is then temporarily immune for 10 minutes.                       Critical Success         The target is unaffected                   Success         The target spends the first action on its next turn with the confused condition                   Failure         The target is confused for 1 minute                   Critical Failure         The target is confused permanently                                    Fabricated Truth                                   Epic                            Incapacitation              Mental              Spell                                Cost         10 Mana              Range         100 feet              Targets         Up to 5 creatures              Save         Will              Duration         Varies                  Choose a single statement you want the targets to believe. The fact can be narrow, wide-reaching, or conceptual, and can be completely unreasonable or ridiculous. If the statement changes what a target perceives, they treat the change as a sudden revelation. The effect of the spell depends on the targets’ Will saves.                       Critical Success         The target doesn’t believe the statement, and it knows you tried to trick it                   Success         The target doesn’t believe the statement or realize you tried to trick it                   Failure         The target believes the statement for a duration of 1 week                   Critical Failure         The target believes the statement with unlimited duration",
        "url": "/illusionist.html"
      }
      
